---
title: Oven-Roasted Lemon Chicken with Hearty Vegetables, Quinoa and Lemon-Thyme Pan Sauce
description: Nothing says winter comfort food like herby roasted chicken and veggies. A combination of parsnips, Brussels sprouts, and carrots is a hearty medley. Served over quinoa and drizzled with a lemony pan-sauce, you’ll be licking your plate clean!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/oven-roasted-lemon-chicken-349ff776.jpg
